pageContext.claim: “Tester, nobody wanted even to contest it. Well, look at what happened in North Dakota with Heidi. Heidi, they said don't contest. One year ago, when we were looking, they all said don't contest Heidi, she can't be beat. She lost by a lot.”
pageContext.analysis: Both races in Montana and North Dakota were considered highly competitive in 2018 given that Trump easily won those states in 2016.
